<paragraph blockId="168.[189,1399,1210,1272]" pageId="168" pageNumber="169">
The specific epithet is from the Latin ‘ 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Steenis &amp; Hippa &amp; Mutin" authorityYear="2018" box="[637,753,1210,1236]" class="Insecta" family="Syrphidae" genus="Sphegina" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="168" pageNumber="169" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="strigillata">
